list.s: [Jack stands stiffly in the shadows under some steps, between two lighted windows]
[a white dress floats by the cabin window, outside]
[they all rush to the window of the cabin and look out]
[they all see the dress float by the cabin window, on its second pass]
[the men go outside to see the dress that was floating by the window]
[Mercer is looking through a mounted telescope to outside the window]
